question: Show me children's books and young adult books illustrated by Jane Smith.
sql_query1:
SELECT Book.title 
FROM Book
WHERE (Book.age_group = "Children's Book" OR Book.age_group = "Young Adult Book") AND Book.illustrator = "Jane Smith"
sql_query2:
SELECT Book.title 
FROM Book
WHERE Book.age_group = "Children's Book" OR Book.age_group = "Young Adult Book" AND Book.illustrator = "Jane Smith"
interpretation1: What children's books were illustrated by Jane Smith and what young adult books were also illustrated by her?
interpretation2: List all children's books and also list young adult books illustrated by Jane Smith.
